('Analytics Dashboard', 'Data Visualization', 'Create an advanced analytics dashboard that provides real-time insights into user behavior, engagement metrics, and conversion funnels. Include customizable widgets and export capabilities.', 'NEW', 'Rachel Green', 'Rachel Green', '2025-11-03 11:20:00', '2025-11-08 09:10:00'),
